HEADWORD: nonwashable
<hw>nonwashable</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>not washable; damaged by
washing; -- used mostly of clothing, especially clothing that must be
cleaned by a dry-cleaning process. Opposite of
<ant>washable</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

